OL,3,C1,400 officers and staff removed from
OL,4,Cpolice force as it uncovers wrongdoing
OL,6,FBritain's biggest police force has
OL,7,Fremoved more than 1,400 officers and
OL,8,Fstaff from its ranks in three years as
OL,9,Fit adopts an "Al Capone" approach to
OL,10,Funcover wrongdoing.
OL,12,FThe clearout, sparked in the wake of
OL,13,Fthe murder of Sarah Everard by a
OL,14,Fserving officer, is the largest in the
OL,15,Fforce's history.
OL,17,FFigures show that 1,442 staff and
OL,18,Fofficers were sacked, or resigned or
OL,19,Fretired between 2022 and June 2025.
