OL,6,FThe annual number rose from 146 in
OL,7,F2021 to 557 in 2024.
OL,9,FThe Metropolitan Police Federation
OL,10,Fsaid officers were being "punched,
OL,11,Fkicked, spat at, driven at and
OL,12,Fstabbed" and "deserve the backing of
OL,13,Ftheir chief officers".
OL,15,FThe staff association added that
OL,16,F"comparing colleagues to American
OL,17,Fgangsters" made the "work of our
OL,18,Fofficers in the capital harder".
