OL,6,FInvestigators are examining the number
OL,7,Fof grievances lodged against different
OL,8,Fsquads along with data including the
OL,9,Fnumber of sick days taken and whether
OL,10,Fthe amount of overtime is justified.
OL,12,FDeputy Commissioner Matt Jukes: "In
OL,13,Fthe same way we would take a sort of
OL,14,FAl Capone approach to tackling
OL,15,Forganised criminality, we're taking
OL,16,Fthat same 360 degree view of
OL,17,Fmisconduct.
