OL,6,F"Looking at questions like sickness,
OL,7,Fgrievances, looking at monitoring
OL,8,Fofficers' use of devices so that we
OL,9,Fcan hold individuals to account,
OL,10,Fbringing all of that information
OL,11,Ftogether to identify officers and
OL,12,Fstaff who are of the greatest concern."
OL,14,FHe said the amount of overtime taken
OL,15,Fcan mean there is a problem.
OL,17,FMr Jukes said: "Overtime and money are
OL,18,Fa big driver of people's motivation.
