OL,6,F"So, it's looking for those signals
OL,7,Fthat tell us we've got problem places
OL,8,Fand problem people."
OL,10,FEarlier this month, nine officers
OL,11,Fbased at Charing Cross were suspended
OL,12,Famid an investigation into excessive
OL,13,Fuse of force and another two removed
OL,14,Ffrom frontline duty.
OL,16,FThe allegations first emerged after an
OL,17,Finvestigation by BBC Panorama.
OL,19,FThe entire custody team at the station
OL,20,Fis being disbanded as the police
OL,21,Finquiry continues.
