OL,6,FCharing Cross was at the centre of a
OL,7,Fseparate controversy when it emerged
OL,8,Fofficers had been involved in
OL,9,Fexchanging obscene and highly
OL,10,Foffensive WhatsApp messages, some of
OL,11,Fthe content of which was too extreme
OL,12,Fto print.
OL,14,FSeparately, four officers have been
OL,15,Farrested and a fifth charged as part
OL,16,Fof an inquiry into their handling of a
OL,17,Fsexual assault allegation against a
OL,18,Fcolleague.
