OL,6,FFour of the officers are based in the
OL,7,Farea squad for north-west London while
OL,8,Fthe fifth is in the Met's internal
OL,9,Fstandards department.
OL,11,FSir Mark Rowley said there are "toxic
OL,12,For corrupt networks or cliques" that
OL,13,Fmight be resistant to change in the
OL,14,Fforce.
OL,16,FA review of the culture in the Met by
OL,17,FBaroness Casey in the wake of Sarah
OL,18,FEverard's murder found that the unit
OL,19,Fwhere killer Wayne Couzens was based
OL,20,Fwas a "dark corner" of the Met.
