OL,6,F"They are being punched, kicked, spat
OL,7,Fat, driven at and stabbed.
OL,9,F"They deserve the backing of their
OL,10,Fchief officers. Not a seemingly
OL,11,Fconstant diatribe from the top of the
OL,12,FMetropolitan Police that drags our
OL,13,Fproud police officers through the mud.
OL,15,F"The language and terminology used by
OL,16,Fthe Deputy Commissioner today `
OL,17,Fcomparing colleagues to American
OL,18,Fgangsters ` makes the work of our
OL,19,Fofficers in the capital harder.
