OL,6,F"It tarnishes them. It is appalling.
OL,7,FOur officers do not deserve it. It
OL,8,Flowers already low morale. It is not
OL,9,Ffair and it is not just.
OL,11,F"The good, brave and hard-working
OL,12,Fcolleagues the Metropolitan Police
OL,13,FFederation represents are the first to
OL,14,Fsay that the very small minority of
OL,15,Fofficers who are not fit to serve
OL,16,Fshould not be in the police service.
OL,18,F"If officers are proven to be guilty
OL,19,Fof criminal offences or serious gross
OL,20,Fmisconduct, then we do not want these
OL,21,Findividuals in the job.
