OL,6,F"However this message from police
OL,7,Fleaders that colleagues should be
OL,8,Fguilty until proven innocent is not
OL,9,Facceptable. Police officers ` like all
OL,10,Fpeople ` have the right to
OL,11,Frepresentation and due process.
OL,13,F"Everyone should be working together
OL,14,Fto move the Metropolitan Police
OL,15,Fforward and make it a proud
OL,16,Forganisation again that people want to
OL,17,Fbe part of and want to serve in."
